<answer>The x-intercepts are, approximately, $(0.1\pm 4.7,0)$. Here is my work:
[[asy]**asy**
unitsize(0.2 cm);
xaxis(-5,9);

yaxis(-7,2);

real f(real x)

{

return -1/9*(x-2)^2+1;
}

